body_html:
The only failure is on Windows CMAKE which seems to be a Jenkins network issue:

22:45:53  > git fetch --tags --progress https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow.git +refs/pull/*:refs/remotes/origin/pr/*
22:45:57 ERROR: Error fetching remote repo 'origin'
22:45:57 hudson.plugins.git.GitException: Failed to fetch from https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow.git
22:45:57 	at hudson.plugins.git.GitSCM.fetchFrom(GitSCM.java:817)
22:45:57 	at hudson.plugins.git.GitSCM.retrieveChanges(GitSCM.java:1084)

I think a rerun may resolve it.
